Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,字幕制作{\b1\c&HC08000&}墨迹未干╰{\c\b}\NQQ:574855297
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:07.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an8}2010年 在发生过一系列无法解释的事情后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:11.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an8}包括牧场主８岁大的孩子离奇失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这个“皮行者牧场”开始备受媒体关注
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:26.22,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,现代国防企业（MDE）派遣了一组专家前往记录和研究这个现象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:38.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an8}MDE录像被发现在一位叫做雅各布朗戴尔斯\N的记者手里，他通过秘密的资源渠道获得的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:39.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,2013年1月18日，朗戴尔斯意外失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:47.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,警告：接下的录像可能会对一些观众造成不适。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an3}2010年11月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,11月11日，这天是科迪特殊的日子\NThis is Cody's special day,November 11th
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:01:00.03,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,跳啊\NJump.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:03.03,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,爸爸！爸爸！\NDad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:04.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，我就在这\NWell, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:07.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,等等，今天是你生日吗？\NWait, is it your birthday today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:09.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你答应会做到的！你答应会做到的！\NYou got to make it!You got to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:14.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我告诉你了啊，我告诉你我会帮你准备的！\NI told you.I told you I would get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:15.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,生日快乐！\NHappy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:21.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在你下个生日我给你请一整个棒球队来这儿\NNext birthday we'll have a whole team of guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:25.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,到时候我们就一起在这儿打棒球\NWe'll all be playing baseball together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,准备好！\NGet set.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:28.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,跑起来!\NGo！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:32.36,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊...\NArgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我有点拉伤，我应该...\NI pulled a muscle.Got to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:41.28,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,什么...那到底是什么鬼东西？\NWhat...What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪？科迪？\N- Cody?- Cody?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:44.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪？科迪！\NCody? Cody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:46.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:55.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,2011年8月1日，MDE开始展开调查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不，我认为霍伊特对此没有任何办法。\NNah, I don't think Hoyt had anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:13.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，孩子突然失踪让人痛心，但这也是事实。\NUh, sad but true,kids are kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，就在那发生后，你知道的\NWell, right after it happened,'cause, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:19.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这些事情致使他被无奈的送进了法院\Nthey had to, like, drag him into court and all that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.41,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以在大家面前他很无助，还有对这些事情\Nso he's kind of forced to be around everybody and all that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.05,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你知道的，不同的是他对这件事情有另外的看法。\Nthere was a difference. And there was some mean in him then, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:28.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,直到那次我遇见一个醉鬼，才提醒我记起他来着\NI didn't consider him, up until that time, a drunkard or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,后来我们有次去递送干草，他还有没从阴影走出来\NI didn't talk to him at length about it, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:34.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以你知道的，关于这个我没怎么过问\Nwe were delivering hay, and he was just broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:38.09,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你知道，要让我亲身经历我才会相信的\NYou know,show it to me and then I'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:41.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你问我，我认为他...他很愧疚\NYou ask me, I think he's... he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:44.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,也许每个人对霍伊特都感到恐惧\NMaybe everybody's projecting their fear on Hoyt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,也许那都是注定的\NMaybe that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那就是他独自生活的缘由\NThat's why he's left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但是在他找到孩子前他都会住在那儿的\NBut he's staying there until he finds his boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说很可悲，真的很可悲。\NI mean, it's sad.It's sad as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.31,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我也有孩子和外孙\NI've got kids and grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,要是我的一个8岁的外孙不见了的话，我应该....\NAnd if an 8-year-old grandkid of mine disappeared, I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，我不知道我该干嘛\NYeah, I don't know what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.29,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪和我年幼的女儿在一个班\NCody was in my little girl's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你要知道，我几乎每天晚上去她的房间里\NI've been having to go in and sleep with her almost every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,陪着她直到她睡着。\Nyou know, 'til she falls asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以呢，嗯，很不容易\NSo, yeah, it's been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.40,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,当然了，伙计，我认识科迪\NOf course, I know Cody, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他可是个好孩子，还很有趣\NHe's a good kid.Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:24.57,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那个小不点本该健健康康成长的\NLittle wiry. He was gonna grow into them feet one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的,伙计\NYeah, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:31.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的,我认识科迪\NYeah. I knew Cody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.02,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说我多少了解他一点\NI mean,I've followed it quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:42.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我真的不买你的账, 我对超自然现象不感兴趣\NI don't really buy either one. I'm not into the paranormal stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:46.36,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我没看过那卷磁带, 我也没看过像那样的狼\NI've never seen that tape. And I've never seen a wolf like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯...\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但这些可能还会发生\NBut it could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果这些事情还会在哪儿发生的话，那就在这儿\NCould happen around here if it's going to happen somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那....你知道的，我不相信这一整件事\NThat's... I don't believe any of it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我必须要看到什么才会相信的\NI got to see something to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我没见过像那样的东西\NI've never seen anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:07.05,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计，你呆在这的话你会看到什么的\NYou stick around, man,you'll see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:19.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,2011年8月2号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我叫萨姆格林\NMy name is Sam green.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是个来自芝加哥大学的\NI'm a PH.D.In socio-cultural anthropology
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,社会文化人类学博士.我已经为MDE做\Nfrom the university of Chicago. I've been working for MDE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,实地科学家大约有6个月了.\Nfor about six months as a field scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.68,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我的伙计\NMy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，萨姆！\NHey, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:44.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哥们，最近怎么样？\NHow are you, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 伙计很高兴见到你。 - 我也是。\N- Good to see you, man.- You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我叫做卡梅隆墨菲，嗯...\NMy name's Cameron Murphy. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是来自洛城的前线记者\NI'm an investigative journalist from Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:53.79,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我和萨姆一起长大，大约一个月前他通知我\NSam and I grew up together.He called me about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:58.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,告诉我说他正前往一个奇怪的牧场进行一项实地调查。\NTold me he was heading up an investigation to some strange cattle ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:02.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,问我会不会来这儿以第三方的视角关注这件事情\NAsked me if I would come out and observe it from a third party perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，这是我们的摄像师布莱顿\NHey, this is our videographer Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，伙计。卡梅隆，很高兴见到你。\NHey, man. Cameron. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.28,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我叫做布莱顿斯洛恩。我是个自由职业的摄像师\NMy name's Britain Sloan. I'm a freelance cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,一般来说不喜欢站在摄像头前\NNormally don't like to be in front of the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以我会简短点\NSo I'll make this short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:16.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在和其他组员在一起前，我干过这个\NI've done this kind of work before with other groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:20.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们从来没遇到过奇怪的或者违常理的事情\NAnd we've never come across anything strange or out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:23.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以我希望这次出行会有点不一样\NSo I hope this trip is a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.36,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗨，伙计，你能帮他拿下包吗？\NHey, man, would you grab his bag for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,当然\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 有劳了，伙计  - 这地儿的小风景怎么样\N- Thanks, man. - How about a little tour of the grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 还可以。 - 知道了\N- Yeah. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特\NHoyt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想你见见我的朋友卡梅隆墨菲\NI want you to meet my friend Cameron Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.24,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,-嘿，卡梅隆。 - 很荣幸见到你，霍伊特\N- Hey, Cameron. - Hoyt, pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.41,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特米勒。那是我的名字，霍伊特米勒\NHoyt Miller. That's my name.Hoyt Miller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，还有，我买下了这，嗯...\NAnd, uh, I bought this, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:47.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这个牧场，哦，有四年...四年多了\NThis ranch, oh, four years... little over four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:52.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你知道的，那时还有着把它改造的想法\Nwith the idea of turning it into something, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:57.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,现在感觉很不一样或者...要我说，嗯...\Nspecial or... say, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:01.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不得不说吗？\NDo I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:05.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我...我现在必须在镜头前说话吗？\NCan I... do I have to talk to the camera right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我真的不是很喜欢这样\NI don't really feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.24,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，大家伙在45分钟内准备好\NAll right, you guys be up in about 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,车子已经备好了\NWe'll have the ATV ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:13.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 听起来很不错。 - 狗儿，过来\N- Sounds good. - Come on, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是我们的主要兽医工作人员丽萨\NThis is our main vet tech Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨，卡梅隆。\NLisa, Cameron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，卡梅隆，我听过很多关于你的事情\NOh, Cameron, I heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:30.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我叫丽萨莫罗，是个实地兽医工作者\NMy name is Lisa Moreau. I'm the field veterinary tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我在这儿工作有些年头了\NI've worked locally for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,几个月前，我刚开始和MDE成员一起工作\NI just started working with MDE a couple months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是和他们在一起我的首件大事\NThis is my first big case with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:42.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们会把我带到这儿是因为我深入研究过这的牛群肢解现象\NThey brought me on because I'm so familiar with the cattle mutilations in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那很烦人\NIt's disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在我的工作上，我见过太多生病和死亡的动物\NI've seen a lot of sick and dead animals in my line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但...这牛群肢解现象...\NBut... The cattle mutilation phenomenon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:56.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我还不能做出合理的解释\NI don't have an explanation for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马的状态还异常吗？\NIs the horse still acting unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，不是。这些马的情绪稳定下来了\NUh, no. The horse's moods stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，他们的行为曾经非常古怪\NUm. Their behavior's been completely erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以，现在一切都好。咱们等等再谈谈\NSo, it's fine now. But you talk to me in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 行，到时候。 - 好的\N- All right, I will. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，你见到马特了吗？\NUh, you seen Matt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.87,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的，我想雷正让他在房子前弄些什么东西\NYeah, I think Ray has him setting up something behind the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 很荣幸见到你，丽萨。 - 见到你很高兴\N- Lisa, pleasure. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.24,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计，你呆在阿富汗有些日子了吧\NThat's a long time to be in Afghanistan, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:24.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,事实上，我加入那十来个士兵的小队\NActually, I was embedded with a group of about 10 soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.31,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,差不多有三个月的时间\Nfor a period of nearly three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 情况还好吗？ - 你是说这些该死的运动传感器吗？\N- How's it going? - You mean, motion sensor hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗨，我叫马特约翰逊。\NHi, I'm Matt Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:35.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我在MDE的媒体实验室工作，我在那儿认识萨姆的\NAnd I work in the media lab at MDE, which is how I met Sam,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他把我带到这儿来进行这项研究\Nwho brought me on board the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:39.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们两对超自然现象都很热衷\NWe both share a passion for the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有，额，我真希望这项研究\NAnd, uh, well, I really hope that this project
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,对这地儿的现象有点帮助\Nhelps legitimize the field a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:50.70,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在队里我担当司机、厨师和该死的队医\NAlso I'm here as the team's driver, cook, and resident bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗？\NYou ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,准备好了。\NCopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我的手，在那上面\NMy hand, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在墙前面走几步，你个蠢蛋\NWalk in front of it, you stupid ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那是雷。我们去看看他。\NThat's Ray. Let's go meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷，来看看卡梅隆墨菲\NRay, I want you to meet Cameron Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，伙计\NHey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计，你是负责传感器这块的吗？\NYou here to help with the sensors, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.87,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷里德，退伍军人\NRay Reed. Ex-military.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:25.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,负责安全和情报还有骂人\NHere for the security and wires and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:29.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果幸运女神眷顾我们有什么发现的话，我们就要在这儿呆上一段时间了\NIf lady luck shines upon us, this place is gonna be a God damn fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那就是我要说的，结束了没？\NThat's all I got. We done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯。\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头弄的怎么样了？\NHow are the cameras coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快好了。你们结束这个后\NThey're almost set up. When you guys are done,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,为什么不去摄像头上露个脸，我会把录像给你看的\Nwhy don't you pop on by and I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:45.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,下午好，霍伊特\NAfternoon, Hoyt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,准备好启程了吗？\NReady to roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.40,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的。大家都上来了没？\NAll right. Everybody in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们这是要去哪？\NWhere we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:03.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特在牧场发现了一头死鹿\NHoyt found a dead deer on the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆想去看看死鹿的情况\NSam wants to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这儿的总面积有多少亩？\NWhat's the acreage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,大约1000亩左右\NAbout 1,000 give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，虽然我下面要说的还没有明确的定义\NWell, it's not clearly defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:25.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但是爱达荷州南部，尤因塔盆地，四角，\NBut parts of Southern Idaho, the Uintah basin, four corners,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,直到内华达州和加利福尼亚都被认为是\Nall the way to Nevada and California is considered
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.70,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,美国超自然现象圣地\Nthe paranormal Mecca of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,今天当地政府甚至从来没有管过这儿\NLocal tribes won't even set foot on this land to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,对于他刚刚说的圣地有什么直接证据吗？\NThere's evidence for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们都知道，嗯，回到18世纪迹象表明\NWe got, uh, evidence going back to the 1800s
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这儿有第一次UFO观光记录\Nwith the first documented UFO sightings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,47年的罗斯威尔事件\NRoswell crash in '47.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:43.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,67年的首次牛群肢解事件\NFirst reported cattle mutilation in '67.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.09,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,达格韦基本上是新的51区\NDugway is basically the new area 51.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.09,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an8}51区：一处极为重要的秘密军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,从没听说过这个\NNever heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:48.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,来这儿途中你刚好经过那儿\NYou passed it right on the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,美国军方研究的爆心投影点\NGround zero for U.S. military research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说我们所谈论的事情都是有人亲眼所见、亲耳所闻的\NI mean, we're talking everything from remote viewing to psychological warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就在那小土丘上面\NJust over the ridge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:33.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，很对不起扫了你的兴。它是自然死亡\NSam, I'm sorry to burst your bubble. But she died of natural causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你注意到它舌头变色了吗？\NDo you see the discoloration in the tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是典型的出血性疾病\NIt's a classic case of hemorrhagic disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,无论怎么都取点样\NTake a sample anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，是你想要的话\NSure, whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，嗯... 我们最好回去\NHey, uh... We'd better get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我感觉有大风暴来临\NWe got a big storm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:53.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,谢谢，霍伊特\NThanks, Hoyt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没事\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所有的生活记录直接上传到这台服务器上\NAll the feeds record directly into the server here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.96,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,以防万一，我把这些都备份在C-70上了\NJust in case, I got it all backed up on the C-70.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,它由发电机供电\NIt's generator powered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是独立的材料制作的，已被设定好了24小时实时监控\NIt's all independently wired, and it's set to record 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头1是一个大范围的道路镜头\NCamera one's a wide shot of the road
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以我们可以监控进出牧场的人\Nso we can monitor everyone coming in and out of the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:18.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头2是房子周边\NCamera two is wide of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头3是西牧场\NCamera three is of the Western pasture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头4是畜栏\NCamera four is of the corral.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头5是饲料仓外部\NCamera five is the barn exterior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,摄像头6就是饲料仓里头\NAnd camera six is inside the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是为了更好配合外部的摄像头\NThat's it for the exterior cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在晚上又是什么情况呢？\NWhat happens at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.03,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们会变成红外摄像头\NThey all switch to infrared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:37.96,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想这就是X射线吧\NThis is the X-ray I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.57,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,真的不是我该管的\NNot really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，让我看看\NOh, let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，给他吧\NWell, just pass it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话，我想和大家伙干上一杯\NIf I could, I'd like to propose a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:50.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，我就想，嗯\NUh, I just want to, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,感谢大家来到这儿\NThank you all for coming up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在我的孩子失踪后，\NSince my boy's been gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:12:00.02,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我得到的帮助很少就快没有了\Nthe help's been few and far between.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:04.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我... 我真的很感谢你们的帮助\NAnd I just... I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想让你们知道这点\NAnd I want you to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事情，我希望大家伙会一直在这儿的\Nwhatever this thing is, I believe it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有那东西很聪明\NAnd it's really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,事实上\NAs a matter of fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我打赌那东西正在注意着我们\NI would bet my arm that it's watching us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，不。不要把我仍在这儿。\NOh, no. Don't leave me up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,干杯吧！\NCheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 干杯      - 干杯\N- Cheers. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:33.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你想我去那儿？\NWhere do you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就走动一下，我好看到你\NJust walk and I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,明白\NCopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是起居室吗？\NThis is the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯。\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,对你的小伙伴说你好\NSay hi to big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快点\NSay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗨\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卧室1\NBedroom one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卧室2\NBedroom two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,用餐间\NThe dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,厨房\NKitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，马特，你可以听我说下楼去吗？\NHey, Matt, can you go downstairs for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,可以。\NYou got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特的房间\NHoyt's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪的房间\NCody's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,来到地下室\NGot the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是老屠宰间\NAnd this is the old butcher room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，我的天\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,抱歉。真的很抱歉\NI'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我没想... 我只是对着摄像头\NI didn't mean... just the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我认为你知道我在这儿\NAnd I thought you knew I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没事。就不要像那样静悄悄的接近人\NIt's all right. Just don't sneak up on people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我知道。那很愚蠢。抱歉\NI know. It was stupid. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 雷，该死的。干这个\N- All right. - This works. God damn it, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计，你刚好呆在盲区\NThe blind spot's going to be on you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果你想看任何录像，和我说就行了\NIf you guys need to review any footage, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我就会把它放到这儿\NAnd I'll set it up right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我可以侦测出牧场大部分区域的运动迹象\NI got motion detectors across most of the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,有什么动静的话，我会知道的\NSo if something moves, we're going to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我也调用了大部分传感器去侦测大型物体\NAlso I programmed most of the sensors to detect only large objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我倒想看看外面的动物们晚上都有些什么活动\NI don't want the local wildlife having us chase ghosts all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,晚安。霍伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的...伙计们明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:20.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那是...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:25.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,有些人认为他造了假录像是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但总有这些怀疑论者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好，要是他真的这么做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,为什么他要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，要是我们有证据的话人们将会认为他疯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.96,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那就是这些人所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.87,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们是来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.29,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,吃你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:50.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an7}用餐间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月2号\NAugust 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是我来这牧场的第一个晚上\NIt's my first official night here at the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.24,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 嗨\N- Hey. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你在这儿自言自语吗？\NAre you in here talking to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.87,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，不。 事实上我是在对着摄像头说话\NUm, no. Actually it's the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我用摄像头来记录行程\NI use it as a video journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.68,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，那笔和纸用来干什么的呢？\NOh. What happened to the days of the mighty pen and paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:16.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 那还是很有用的东西。或者...  - 果断点说，我不需要它们\N- Is that still a thing, or... - Sadly, they are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯。好的，只要你不用这东西\NHmm. Well, as long as you don't use this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:21.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,来大半夜拍照就行\Nfor any midnight photography...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,苍天为证\NScout's honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，好的\NOh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.29,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 我已经录了相了。 - 的确\N- I got that on tape. - You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.80,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 那上面也录了。-好的\N- And tape. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以你认识萨姆多久了？\NSo how long have you known Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,几个月\NA couple months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，额，我真的更希望关掉摄像机\NListen, uh, I actually would prefer this to be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.27,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就是这个按钮\NIt's actually this button.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，谢谢提醒\NWell, that is good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.36,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那该死的是什么？\NWhat the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在屋顶上！\NThey're on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘘\NShh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,该死的到底是什么\NWhat the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:20.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那是...\NIs that the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.31,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘘\Nshh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,该死\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:40.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，我的天。在这儿！在这儿！\NOh, my God. You guys. You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我去拿梯子\NI'll get the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.24,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,布莱顿，小心点上去\NCareful going up, Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,等等，丽萨，什么...\NWait, Lisa, what...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，不要。是蝙蝠\NMatt, don't. Rabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特，你以前从来没遇见过像这样的事情吗？\NYou ever seen anything like that before, Hoyt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,真的没有。没遇见像这样的\NHell no. Nothing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没有任何创伤。内部结构都是完好的\NThere's no trauma. The internal organs are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:34.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是声波扰乱了它们的声纳系统\NIt was definitely the tone that messed with their sonar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，哈\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:40.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这才是刚开始而已\NThis is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想睡下觉\NI'm gonna get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\NGood luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想去记录这个声波事件\NI'm going to document it as the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，没问题\NYeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.90,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我需要你再去看看\NI need you to check more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我已经看过了\NWe've already checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你好。请在一段语音后留下您的录音\Nhello. Please leave a message after the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:15.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你好！米勒先生，我是白橡木精神病院的大夫戴维\NHello, Mr. Miller, this is Dr. David at white oak psychiatric.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想告诉你你妻子这几个月来的进步\NI wanted to talk to you about your wife's progress over the last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果你能在你最方便的时候给我的电话的话\NIf you could give me a call at your earliest convenience,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我会很感激\NI'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:34.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，我的天。对不起\NOh, my God. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的。没事\NOk. It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:03.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 你们都还好吗？ - 是的\N- You guys all right? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，因为我要你们跟着我去牧场\NGood. 'Cause I'm going to need you to follow me out to the pasture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.27,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,发生什么了？\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:14.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,MDE之前没有提到会派其他人来这个牧场啊\NMDE never mentioned anyone else coming up to the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.55,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那不像是他们的作风\NI don't think that's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.02,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他已经在这儿有三四十分钟了\NHe's been sitting out there about 35, 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:22.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没有什么保护层。那是军用车吗？\NThere's no plates on it. Is that thing military?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不知道。我没有头绪\NI don't know. It's hard to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.40,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，也许是某人迷路了呗\NWell, maybe it's someone who got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他开动了。正在掉头呢\NHe's on the move. He's turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:47.31,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，等等，等一下。我有个问题\NSam, wait. Hang on. I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷，你怎么看？\NWhat do you think, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不知道，但是不该那样做的\NI don't know. But it's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，那肯定是不对的\NNo. It sure ain't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,太没礼貌了，我从没见过有人像那样冒然闯进来\NI've never seen anybody out there like that. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.09,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,注意，我是关于这件事情的头儿\NLook, I'm team leader of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:04.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果你是头儿，那你应该知道的\NIf you are the team leader, then you're supposed to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，霍伊特，我不知道来这牧场的每辆车的情况\Nlook, Hoyt, I don't know every vehicle that's going to come on to the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.80,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，冷静。听着，弄清楚先\NHey, calm down. Listen, figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:21.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的。我对昨晚那件噪音事件进行过了分析\NOK, so I ran an analysis on that tone from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,证据表明我们的录像里面真有2道声波\NTurns out there were actually two sounds on that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:27.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,高音调的噪音很显然我们都知道，就是把我们吵醒的那种\NThere was that high-pitched noise that we obviously know, the one that woke us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.29,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但是在这噪音的下面我发现了次声波\NBut below that I found traces of infrasound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:31.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,次声波？\NInfrasound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:33.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的，它的频率比人耳可听见频率范围还低\NYeah, it's a frequency below the audible range of the human ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那什么可以引起像那样的声波\NSo what could cause something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:39.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想，次声波可能自然产生或者人为制造\NI mean, infrasound can occur naturally or it can be manmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你懂的，军方通过每秒特定的周期\NYou know, at certain cycles per second,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,事实上已经成功的制造出了次声波\Nthe military has actually successfully tested infrasound
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:47.41,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,来引起负面影响诸如眩晕，沮丧，恐惧，不安，\Nto cause things like vertigo, depression, fear, anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:51.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,身体病变，咽喉压迫等各种各样的可怕影响\Nphysical lesions, throat pressure, all sorts of awful side effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:54.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说，这些只是我所了解的\NAnd, I mean, those are just the ones that we know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.55,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，那又是怎样自然产生的呢?\NOk. And how about naturally?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:58.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所有我们知道的大型自然灾害\NAll the big natural disasters that we know of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:01.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,火山，地震，雪崩\Nvolcanoes, earthquakes, avalanches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:05.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那就是为什么动物们可以在人们采取措施前侦测地震\NIt's why animals are able to detect earthquakes before people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:06.79,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们可以感觉到振动\NThey pick up the vibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,动物...鲸鱼...它们发出听不见的声波\NAnimals... whales... they use inaudible sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,来麻痹并且抓住特定的猎物，你知道的像鱼这样的\Nto paralyze and catch certain prey, like, you know, fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说我们听马特所说的声音\NI'm just saying that the sound we heard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.70,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,可能是被活着的动物发出的\Nthat Matt's talking about could've been caused by a live animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:19.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,真不知道我们是在这儿做些什么\NWe have no idea what we're dealing with here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:22.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼他妈的怎么跑到这儿来的\NHow the fuck would a whale get up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:40.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们要在这儿干点什么吗？\NSo what are we doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，据说如果直接尝试去\NOh, it's really well documented that attempting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:44.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,和超自然能量交流的话真可以\Nto communicate with paranormal energies directly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:47.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,加大遇见它们的可能性\Nreally increases likelihood of contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,跟我来\NFollow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:51.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,跟在你后边\NAfter you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:10.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆要我来牧场的，并做些祈祷\NSam has asked me to come and do a blessing on the property
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:15.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,以便和这片大地上会私语的能量交流\Nto communicate with the energy that speaks from this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:17.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但你要知道\NBut you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.67,0:23:20.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这片土地被人们遗弃\NThis land is forsaken by my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这只是试着给你们带来\NAnd it's only to try and bring you some protection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,一些我能做到的保护\Nthat I've agreed to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:28.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这儿有勇士们在这山谷里打猎\NThere are legends of warriors hunting in this valley,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:33.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,回到他们变得凌乱不堪的部落的传说\Nreturning to their tribe disturbed and changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:37.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,并且整个部落消失的故事\NStories of whole tribes disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:41.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这片土壤充满这黑暗\NThere is a darkness in this soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:44.79,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果不叫你们离开可能你们感觉无关紧要\NI would not feel right if I didn't suggest that you leave now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:49.80,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,或者这样说，这个地方除了给你们带来灾难之外一无是处\Nor to say that this place has nothing for you but suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:54.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我也知道你们已经决定留在这儿\NI also know that you've chosen to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:58.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能给这里多带来一点希望，不管有多少\NAnd I'll do what I can to bring some light here, no matter how small.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:07.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在我和我的祖先联系的时候我需要你们保持沉默\NI ask for silence now while I reach out to my ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.79,0:24:49.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,噢，噢。\NAhh. Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.29,0:24:54.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还好吗？还能呼吸吗？\NAre you ok? Can you breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.57,0:25:01.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆\NSam.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:15.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我无能为力\NThere's nothing I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.58,0:25:17.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们他妈的得离开这儿\NYou need to get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.31,0:25:31.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月4号
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.07,0:25:39.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，4号凌晨一点\NUh, 1:00 A.M. on the 4th.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.54,0:25:43.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嗯，这么多个晚上的事情后已经没睡过好觉了\NUm, already low on sleep after the events of the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.91,0:25:46.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆认为我们离具体的那东西越来越近\NSam seems to think we're close to getting something concrete,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.88,0:25:49.05,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,某... 某种迹象\Nsome... some kind of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.05,0:25:51.75,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我承认那个声音，死蝙蝠...\NI admit the sound, the dead bats...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.75,0:25:54.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,的确很奇怪\Nstrange, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.69,0:25:57.56,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,超自然吗？\NParanormal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.56,0:25:59.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不是很确定\NI'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.86,0:26:02.90,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,等一下\NHang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.03,0:26:07.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,又怎么了？\NSo what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.37,0:26:08.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,过来，雷发现了什么东西\NRay's got something. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.08,0:26:19.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以我们发现什么了\NSo what do we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.71,0:26:21.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就在刚刚，巨大的某种东西触发了\NJust a second ago, something very large set off
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.48,0:26:23.02,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,盲区的一个传感器\None of the sensors in the blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.02,0:26:24.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,具体的说是在三区\NZone three, specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.82,0:26:26.95,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以我们说的是比鹿还大的东西\NSo we're talking about something bigger than a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.95,0:26:29.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快赶上该死的直升机那么大了\NTry the size of a god damn helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.07,0:26:41.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.67,0:26:43.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卡梅隆，检查这区域远侧\NCameron, check the far side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.97,0:26:46.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,剩下的人，跟着我\NThe rest of you guys, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.62,0:27:36.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,到这儿来\NOver here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.04,0:27:54.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这不是自然死亡\NThis is not a natural death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.78,0:27:56.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,动物攻击什么的吗？\NWhat about an animal attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.88,0:28:01.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，不。这儿没有咬痕和爪痕。\NOh, no. There are no bite marks, no claw marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.12,0:28:05.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这些切口都是完美的\NThese incisions, they're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.15,0:28:07.09,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,抱歉，小家伙\NSorry, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.13,0:28:15.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没有血了\NNo blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.60,0:28:18.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这几乎是外科手术\NIt's almost surgical.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.87,0:28:21.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,该死的\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:22.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，我想把这个小家伙带回去看看\NAll right, I want to bag the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.94,0:28:25.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，拿袋子过来\NMatt, get the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.58,0:28:32.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.51,0:28:35.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，给点劲，想干嘛的话快点\NCome on, Sam, if you're going to do it, do it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.00,0:29:34.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月12号
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.14,0:29:35.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，丽萨\NHi, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.68,0:29:37.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，萨姆。嘿，布莱顿\NHey, Sam. Hey, Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.95,0:29:39.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.28,0:29:41.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,血？\NBlood?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.85,0:29:44.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，是的。我昨晚流鼻血了\NOh, yeah. I had a nosebleed last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.99,0:29:46.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你很容易出鼻血吗？\NYou prone to nose bleeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.99,0:29:49.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,额，不是的。\NUh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.12,0:29:51.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,自从来这儿有过几次了\NAnd I've had a couple since I've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.16,0:29:53.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想是这儿海拔的原因或者...\NI'm thinking it's just the elevation or...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.89,0:29:55.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,也许吧\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.70,0:29:59.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,布莱顿，过来\NCome on, Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:07.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,因为她有过几次流鼻血你才知道去查看录像吗？\NAnd you knew to check the tape because she had a few bloody noses?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.84,0:30:09.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,只是一种感觉\NJust a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.74,0:30:11.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想我们不能告诉他\NI don't think we can tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.95,0:30:14.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,告诉他什么？你怎么解释这个？\NTell him what? How would you even explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.11,0:30:18.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不必了。你还想看到更疯狂的东西吗？\NYou don't. You want to see something even crazier?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.72,0:30:22.05,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是9号的录像\NThis is a tape from the 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.06,0:30:24.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月8号\NAugust 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.12,0:30:26.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，我的天\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.73,0:30:30.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月7号。每个晚上11点11分\NAugust 7th. 11:11 every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.73,0:30:32.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷，现在是什么时间？\NRay, what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.17,0:30:34.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,现在是11点过9分\NIt's 11:09.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.87,0:30:40.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，什么时候了?\NWhat time is it, Matt?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.64,0:30:42.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快10分了。雷，看着摄像头。\NIt's almost 10 after. Ray, check the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.18,0:30:43.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,大家伙，发生什么事情了？\NYou guys, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.98,0:30:45.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛？萨姆，发生什么事情了？\NWhat are you guys doing? Sam, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.78,0:30:47.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，我要你给我精确数到11点11分\NMatt, I need you to give me an exact count up to 11:11.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.78,0:30:49.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？ - 好的。摄像头就绪。\N- You understand? - All right, camera's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.12,0:30:50.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？ - 摄像头就绪\N- Why? - Camera's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.99,0:30:53.09,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 我们现在还多久？ - 现在还有一分钟\N- Where are we at right now? - You're at a minute right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.09,0:30:54.75,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 你们这是在干嘛？ - 你能出来一会儿吗？\N- What are you guys doing? - Can you come outside for just a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.76,0:30:56.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,可以，可以，好的。等一会儿。你们在干嘛？\NSure. Sure. Yeah. Wait a minute. What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.32,0:30:58.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,等等。这是我的房子。你们这是在干嘛？\NWait a second! This is my house.What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.99,0:31:02.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，看看吧。在过去的几个夜晚精确到11点11分的时候\NAll right, look, the last couple of nights at exactly 11:11,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.66,0:31:04.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,有能量穿过房子\Nenergy has moved through the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.30,0:31:06.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，就还有45秒\NSam, you're at 45 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.00,0:31:09.70,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 房子里面的能量？ - 是的\N- An energy in this house?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.70,0:31:12.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你说“能量”是什么意思？你到底在说什么？\NWhat do you mean "an energy"? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.38,0:31:16.27,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 不，我们不需要... - 我们不需要拿枪\N- No, we don't need... - You don't need the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.78,0:31:21.28,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还多久？30秒？\NWhere we at? 30 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.28,0:31:23.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，不论你们看到什么\NAll right, no matter what you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.18,0:31:25.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不论大家伙看到什么，摄像头都会第一时间记录下来\Nno matter what you guys see, the camera goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.72,0:31:27.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我正要放下呢\NI'm putting it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.19,0:31:29.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.86,0:31:32.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，我们还有10... 9... 8...\NOk, we're at 10... 9... 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.86,0:31:36.80,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,7... 6... 5...\N7... 6... 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.20,0:31:42.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,现在是11点11分\N11:11.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.77,0:31:48.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没什么嘛！\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.34,0:31:53.75,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪！科迪！\NCody! Cody!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.75,0:31:55.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪！科迪！\NCody! Cody!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.82,0:31:58.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿，科迪！科迪！\NHey, Cody! Cody!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.39,0:31:59.95,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪，来和我说说话啊，是爸爸\NCody, buddy, it's daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.26,0:32:05.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，后退点。\NSam, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.46,0:32:11.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪！\NCody!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.87,0:32:13.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪。\NCody.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.18,0:32:32.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪！\NCody!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.32,0:32:35.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪？\NCody?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.95,0:33:05.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，丽萨\NMatt, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.09,0:33:09.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,进来。\NGet in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:13.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么？\NWhat the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.26,0:33:15.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，你去拿好装备\NMatt, you go, get her kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.40,0:33:18.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们需要记录所有的这些\NWe need to cast all these prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.27,0:33:23.03,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,看看这些痕迹。它们到底从哪儿来？\NLook at all these tracks. Where did they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.92,0:33:39.95,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这些一定是犬的脚印\NThese are definitely canine prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.95,0:33:41.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但它太大了\NBut they're enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:48.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 有任何发现吗？- 还没有\N- Anything?  - Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.53,0:33:50.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特怎么了？\NHow's Hoyt?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.93,0:33:52.56,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不论好坏，现在他在借酒消愁呢\NFor better or worse, he's got a lot of alcohol in him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.57,0:33:54.40,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那似乎他像是冷静下来了咯\NBut it seems like he's calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.80,0:34:00.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,大家伙注意，我有发现\NYou guys, I got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.22,0:34:11.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这上面说“仅供紧急情况”\NIt says "for emergencies only."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.30,0:34:30.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，那到底是什么？\NWhat the hell is that, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.37,0:34:36.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,打个电话现在\NMake a call right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.58,0:34:38.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆\NSam!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.35,0:34:40.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,无人接听\NNo one's picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.58,0:34:42.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,现在还有他们其他的号码吗？\NDo you have another number for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.25,0:34:44.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.25,0:34:45.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 萨姆，有人... - 丽萨，你想我干嘛\N- Sam, someone's... - What do you want me to do, Lisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.52,0:34:47.95,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说...\NI'm just saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.42,0:34:51.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的\Nyeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.99,0:34:54.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我的确是打了电话\NI did call, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.06,0:34:56.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好，我们...\NWell, what we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.16,0:34:57.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你是说他们到过这儿？\Nyou're saying they were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.60,0:35:00.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 从67年到71年。 -做什么？\N- From '67 to '71. - Doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.47,0:35:04.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,注意，你们都搞错了，好吗？\NLook, you guys are looking at this the wrong way, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.17,0:35:05.87,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们回答了我所有的问题\NThey answered all my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.87,0:35:07.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们主动提供文档记录\NThey offered to provide documentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.47,0:35:09.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们不是想试着去隐瞒什么\NThey're not trying to hide anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.18,0:35:12.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们真那么做了？他们回答了你全部问题... 什么问题？\NThey did? They answered your question... your questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.11,0:35:14.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你到底在说神马？\NWhat the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.25,0:35:16.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特，他们回答了我所有的问题\NThey answered all my questions, Hoyt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.12,0:35:19.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我的天，他们真的那样做了吗？\NMy goodness gracious, they did?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.42,0:35:21.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们没有找到任何东西，好吗？\NThey didn't find anything, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.39,0:35:23.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我现在想和你谈谈\NI want to talk to you for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.46,0:35:25.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们到过这！到过这！\NThey were here. They were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.46,0:35:28.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,等等。等等。且听我一言。\NWait. Wait. Just listen to me one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.20,0:35:29.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 听我说！ - 马特\N- Listen to me! - Matt!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.20,0:35:30.53,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们到过这儿？\NThey were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.53,0:35:32.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你是要说他们到过这儿吧\NYou're telling me they were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.20,0:35:35.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在我的孩子被带走前，他们就到过这儿了\NThey were here before my boy was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.00,0:35:36.57,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,一切为了科学。\NBetter science.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.57,0:35:38.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你就会嚷嚷。你就会嚷嚷\NYou're just talking. You're just talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.97,0:35:41.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你能说到什么。别在这儿给我扯淡了\NYou're not saying anything. You just say, "blah, blah, blah."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.11,0:35:43.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那就是你能做的。你只会嚷嚷\NThat's the way you live your life. You just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.58,0:35:45.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是在讨论这儿的真人真事\NI'm talking about something real here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.55,0:35:47.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我在谈论我的孩子的事\NI'm talking about my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.38,0:35:50.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，在打了那个电话之后我才有头绪\NLook, we had no idea until I just had that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:53.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但是他们继续呆在这对你的孩子也无能为力\NBut them being here has nothing to do with your boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.62,0:35:55.45,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,理解吗？霍伊特？\NYou understand, Hoyt?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.46,0:35:58.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么对我的孩子无能为力？告诉我？\NWhy? Why does it have nothing to do with my boy? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.59,0:36:00.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你... 你能告诉我吗？\NDo... do you have an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.06,0:36:02.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.00,0:36:05.70,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨，你可是个科学家\NLisa, you are a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.63,0:36:11.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们来调查什么？想试着发现什么？\NWhat are you investigating? What are you trying to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.54,0:36:14.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们是来帮我找回孩子的吗？\NAre you trying to find my boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.11,0:36:16.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们是来帮我找回儿子的吗？\NAre you trying to find my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.51,0:36:19.95,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,看着我的眼睛告诉我你们是来帮我找回儿子的\NJust look me in the eye and tell me that you're trying to find my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.95,0:36:21.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们是来帮我找回儿子的吗？\NAre you trying to find my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.62,0:36:23.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 我是来帮你的。 - 那你怎么帮我呢？\N- I'm trying to help you. - How you trying to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.65,0:36:26.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你来这儿只是为了一己私欲的吧。\NYou're trying to help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.15,0:36:28.02,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我已经看透你了\NI'm on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.32,0:36:32.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你最好得当心点了\NYou'd better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.13,0:36:34.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,最好得当心你自个了啊\NYou'd better watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.73,0:36:39.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,放下吧。\NPut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.34,0:36:50.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这就是我要说的\NThis is what I was telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:52.28,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计们，我发现在窝棚下面埋了两个箱子\NGuys, I found two more containers buried in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.28,0:36:54.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我要说的是，发现的第一个箱子里有一根毛\NNow, one was empty like the first one I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.15,0:36:56.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但是第二个里面就藏有这个\NBut the second had this in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.72,0:36:59.22,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么？ - 这是卷录像带\N- What is this? - It's a U-matic tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.22,0:37:01.75,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在60年代末和70年代初很流行\NMostly used in the late '60s and early '70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.76,0:37:03.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有，萨姆，这刚好和MDE说的\NAnd, Sam, that would correspond to the timeframe
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.62,0:37:06.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他们首次来这儿的时间段吻合\Nthat MDE said they were originally on the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.13,0:37:09.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不是很清楚我们是否能通过网上的信息来弄明白里面的内容\NI'm not sure offhand if we have anything on site I can check this with.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.40,0:37:12.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我看看能在里面找到些什么，好吗？\NI'll see what I can put together, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.17,0:37:19.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月12号，深夜\NLate night. August 12th.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:23.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好像MDE在60年代派过人到这儿调查过些事情\NApparently MDE was out here in the '60s looking into this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.74,0:37:28.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们在窝棚下找到的箱子上面写了“仅供紧急情况”\NThe box we found in the shed said "for emergencies only."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:31.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,里面什么都没有\NAnd it was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.32,0:37:34.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我现在，嗯，更关心的是\NI would, uh, probably be more concerned about that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.12,0:37:37.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好像我都还没看清楚霍伊特的儿子长什么样子\Nif I hadn't seen what looked like Hoyt's son
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.42,0:37:39.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他就穿过了房子\Ntear through the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.53,0:37:42.79,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,去了窝棚里面，消失的无影无踪\Ngo into a shed, and completely disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:46.80,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他就那样消失了。我... 我无法解释\NHe was gone. I... I can't explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.80,0:37:49.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我认为萨姆是这么的痴迷去找到\NI feel like Sam is so obsessed with finding evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.64,0:37:51.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这儿所发生的事情的迹象\Nabout what's happening here
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.34,0:37:55.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,以致他都没有去质疑过MDE的动机\Nthat he won't even question MDE's motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.14,0:38:04.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月14号
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.39,0:40:30.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.84,0:40:46.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,所以，丽萨，你从来没看过那样的东西吗？\NSo, Lisa, you've never seen anything like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.58,0:40:48.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.65,0:40:54.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就是这个\NThat's it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.69,0:40:56.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们去活捉他\NLet's go hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.41,0:41:20.68,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这儿应该有线索，对吧？\NThere should be tracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.68,0:41:23.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我觉着我们应该找找和窝棚里一样的线索\NI think we should be looking for the tracks we found in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.78,0:41:26.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,肯定还是那头怪兽\NIt has to be the same animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.25,0:41:29.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,以我们所见的狼的标准来对比的话\NAnd just judging by the size of the wolf we saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.59,0:41:32.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这家伙快有500英镑重了，有狼五倍那么大\NI'd say it was easily 500 pounds, which is five times larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.73,0:41:34.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,大家伙！\NGuys!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.03,0:41:37.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那东西超大\NThat thing is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.37,0:41:43.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,给点劲，我们过去瞧瞧\NCome on, let's go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.84,0:41:45.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,给点劲，这就是我们来这儿的目的。走起\NCome on, that's what we're here for. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.78,0:42:28.45,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,现在我们最好步行过去，他就在那儿\NWe got to go the rest of the way on foot, he's right out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.45,0:42:30.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，走吧\NAll right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.62,0:42:33.32,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,放轻松，现在\NEasy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.02,0:42:36.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,放轻松，现在\NEasy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.48,0:43:00.41,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,看看那个，我现在真想回去\NLook at that. I want to go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.95,0:43:06.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.72,0:43:07.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,放轻松。等等。慢一点。我要去那儿\NEasy. Wait. Slow down. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.92,0:43:09.55,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,小心点！小心点！\NCareful! Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.56,0:43:11.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特，它去哪了？\NHoyt, where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.76,0:43:15.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我也没看见。小心为好\NI don't see it. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.83,0:43:17.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计们，到这儿来\NGuys, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.93,0:43:20.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,等等，萨姆，你看到这个洞口了吗？\NWait, Sam, did you see the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.57,0:43:25.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 那有个洞口\N- What is it?  - There was a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.71,0:43:30.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我打赌这是个岩洞\NI bet it's a cave system.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.38,0:43:32.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我车上有些绳子。我去拿绳子\NI got some ropes in my truck. Let me go get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.98,0:43:35.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 好的。 - 你们小心点\N- All right.  - You guys be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.38,0:43:36.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那头怪兽还呆在这外面呢\NThat thing's still out here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.85,0:44:12.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，这儿你喜欢吧\NSam, you're gonna want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.16,0:44:26.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你说说那个有多少年份了？\NHow old do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.50,0:44:31.04,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,天啊，萨姆，这儿到底发生了什么\NJesus, Sam, what's going on really?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.04,0:44:33.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们看到的到底是什么？\NWhat the hell we even looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.08,0:44:42.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷，看这个！\NRay, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.95,0:44:47.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好像是找到画这些壁画的人了\NLooks like we found our artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.82,0:44:51.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘘。 嘘\NShh. Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.16,0:45:00.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那东西到底是怎么下这儿来的？\NHow the hell would that thing even get down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.60,0:45:04.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊！快跑！快点！\NOh, God! Go!  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.17,0:45:10.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特！\NMatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.08,0:45:11.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快点！快点！我说快点啊！我们快跑！\NCome on! Come on!  I said hurry! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.14,0:45:14.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，绳子！\NMatt, the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.18,0:45:16.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,布莱顿先！快点，关掉摄像机\NBritain first! Come on, turn off the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.69,0:45:24.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月13号。我们...\NAugust 13th. We just...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.69,0:45:31.23,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那头狼，我不知道...\Nthe wolf, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.17,0:45:37.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,早上我们会去了解了解那个壁画的\Ncome and take a closer look at the artwork in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.01,0:45:43.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,可能是维摩那，对吗？\NCould be a vimana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.08,0:45:44.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,什么东西？\NA what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.64,0:45:46.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,维摩那\NA vimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.64,0:45:47.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：维摩那，古代印度神话传说中遨游天空的飞行器。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.18,0:45:48.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊？\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.72,0:45:51.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在印度，出土的古书籍\NIn India, they've uncovered all these ancient texts
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.65,0:45:54.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,和文献描述了一种被称作维摩那的外星飞船\Nand documents that describe a flying spacecraft called a vimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.89,0:45:58.29,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说，他看起来....他看起来和这个蛮相似的\NAnd I mean, it looks... it looks just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.29,0:46:01.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,尽管这些东西在有6000年前就有记载\NEven though that stuff is, like, 6,000 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.06,0:46:02.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,和很多人认为这是神话\Nand a lot of people think it's myth,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.66,0:46:04.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但是你知道的我们这领域的专家认为\Nexperts in our field think that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.76,0:46:07.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就从其画的原理图和飞行路线图来看\Nbased on the schematics and the flight plans and the design
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.17,0:46:11.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,它和我们今天的科技相吻合\Nthat it's as modern as anything you'd see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.20,0:46:14.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你是在猜想我们的先祖在岩洞深处\NAre you suggesting that our native painted a spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.74,0:46:16.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,留下了这些壁画吗？\Non the inside of this cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.94,0:46:18.81,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.31,0:46:22.28,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,正好，我明白我们所看到的了\NJust, I know everything we've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.28,0:46:24.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那的确很难以置信\NThat just seems pretty astounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.12,0:46:25.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 额，那就像是个完美的巧合。 - 还有这狼呢？\N- Well, it's, like, a perfect match.  - And the wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.82,0:46:28.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,体型比那失踪的孩子和一般的狼都大\NThis is bigger than a wolf or missing kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.96,0:46:40.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他会到这儿来\NHow do you even know he's back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.73,0:46:43.80,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他不是正在那忙活他的车子吗\NHe's working on the ATV.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.34,0:46:57.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,刚回到那儿我不是有意那样说的\NJust wanted to say I completely lost my perspective back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.25,0:46:58.95,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有，嗯\NAnd, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.95,0:47:01.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉\NI'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.89,0:47:05.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你知道，像那样事情时有发生\NStuff like that happens sometimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.73,0:47:11.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你知道的，嗯\NYou know, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.17,0:47:20.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪，在他生日的那天，用他在那摘的\NCody, on his birthday, he woke his mother up
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.37,0:47:25.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,一束野花把他妈妈给弄醒了\Nwith a handful of wildflowers he picked in that field right out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.01,0:47:27.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他妈妈看着他，对他说到\NAnd she looked at him, and she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.65,0:47:32.68,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,“乖孩子，做什么呢...今天可是你的生日。为...为什么送我花呢”\N"son, what... it's your birthday. Why... why you giving me flowers?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.69,0:47:38.26,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他就回答道：“是这样，妈妈，因为有你才有我啊”\NAnd he said, "well, because you're the reason I got born, ma."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.63,0:47:43.36,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那孩子本性就这样\NThat's the kind of kid he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.36,0:47:46.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他就这样\NHe is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.00,0:47:48.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪就那样\NThat's Cody.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.90,0:47:55.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，嗯\NListen, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.14,0:47:57.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,很抱歉那晚在桌面上让你难堪了\NI'm sorry I gave you a hard time the other night at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.94,0:48:00.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那... 我不...\NIt's just... I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.78,0:48:04.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我没理解你们所用的方式。还有，嗯....\NI don't understand your techniques. And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.09,0:48:09.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我就想让你们知道我很高兴你们能来这儿\NI just want you to know I appreciate you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.86,0:48:14.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有，嗯\NAnd, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.69,0:48:18.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说，这是唯一给我带来希望的事了\NI mean, it's the only thing that gives me any hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.21,0:49:09.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.03,0:50:03.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没道理啊\NThat doesn't make sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.94,0:50:06.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘘！\NShh!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.42,0:50:26.56,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.93,0:50:37.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月16号
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.60,0:51:42.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,怎么？？\NWhat's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.97,0:51:45.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,牧场摄像头失去信号了\NThe pasture cam's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.50,0:51:47.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特，拿着对讲机过那儿去\NMatt, take this walkie and go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.51,0:51:49.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计，不会耽误多少时间的\NWon't even take you two minutes, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.38,0:51:51.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 好的，萨姆，你能... - 动手啊，马特！\N- All right, Sam, can you... - Just do it, Matt!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.28,0:51:55.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,带我看看室外摄像头的情况\NTake me through all the exterior cams.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.01,0:51:56.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.95,0:52:04.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听得到吗？\NDo you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.59,0:52:07.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,给我离远30英尺。谢谢了，伙计\NGive me 30 feet back for focus. Thanks, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.50,0:52:18.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特？\NMatt?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.44,0:52:19.90,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特！\NMatt!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.91,0:52:21.24,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊！哦，天啊！\NAah! Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.24,0:52:23.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,过去！\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.18,0:52:34.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,马特突然就被那样\NMatt's up and about.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.69,0:52:38.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他伤的挺严重的，但他应该还好\NHe's pretty beat up, but he should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.46,0:52:41.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,霍伊特的狗所发生的事情，我真不能解释\NI have no explanation for what happened to Hoyt's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.60,0:52:46.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卡梅隆，可以听到吗？\NCameron, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.07,0:52:48.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的，抱...歉。\NYeah, I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.04,0:52:53.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,真的，萨姆，给我退后\NSeriously, Sam, just back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.17,0:52:55.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就是这个意思！\NI mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.71,0:53:04.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这样？\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.22,0:53:05.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了？\NWhat the hell is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.52,0:53:08.05,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我被刮起来重重的摔倒在地\NI was just picked up and thrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.05,0:53:10.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有我们对那不可置信的事情，都没有站得住脚的解释\NAnd we don't have a single explanation as to how that's even possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.49,0:53:12.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，我告诉你我决定去干嘛\NLook, let me tell you what's going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.66,0:53:14.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我要去急诊室看看，然后订一张离开这儿的机票\NI'm going to the E.R. then I'm booking a flight out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.73,0:53:17.39,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果你们头脑都清醒的话\NAnd if you guys had, like, an ounce of common sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.40,0:53:19.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,都该跟着我走\Nyou'd all come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.17,0:53:22.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,糟糕，你们可能要换一个司机了，你们另寻他人吧\NYou need another driver so bad, you hire someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.57,0:53:26.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,说真的，大家伙注意安全\NBe careful, guys. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.01,0:53:28.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，你就是个混蛋。知道不？\NYou're an asshole, Sam! You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.51,0:53:30.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,混蛋\NAsshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.31,0:53:38.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们不是还有霍伊特的车子呢\NWe still have Hoyt's truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.75,0:53:43.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们还可搭乘霍伊特的车\NWe can go in Hoyt's truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.33,0:53:52.56,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷，发生什么了？\NSo what's going on, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.57,0:53:56.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你们还记得马特在窝棚找到了有卷录像带的\NAre you guys aware that Matt found additional MDE materials in the shed,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.50,0:53:58.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,MDE材料吗？\Nincluding a videotape?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.54,0:54:01.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,是的，他提过。但是我想那可能太旧了不能播放了吧\NYeah, he mentioned it. But I thought it was too old to play up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.34,0:54:04.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不。事实是我找到了一台老式磁带机\NNo. It turns out I was able to find an old deck
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.54,0:54:06.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,并把他改成一个硬件驱动器了\Nand transfer it to a hard drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.61,0:54:09.41,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好。录像带里有什么内容？\NOk. So what was on the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.28,0:54:15.19,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我想大家来一同欣赏会好一点\NI think it's better if I just play it for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.79,0:54:50.05,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那儿，就在那儿\NThere. Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.41,0:55:16.31,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡，能听到吗？\NRebecca, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.37,0:55:45.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们是在车上和丽贝卡回来的路上\NWe're on our way back in with Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.85,0:55:49.11,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,离开有个八分钟了\NAbout eight minutes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.78,0:56:21.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,妈妈？妈妈？\NMommy? Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.38,0:56:23.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我妈妈呢？\NWhere's mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.22,0:56:25.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽贝卡，这就是我们要弄明白的\NThat's what we're trying to figure out, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.38,0:56:27.52,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你记得你上次和她在一起吗？\NYou remember the last time you were with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.22,0:57:36.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,她走了多远？\NHow far out was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.82,0:57:39.22,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在牧场外边\NWell beyond the pasture.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.23,0:57:41.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,狗呢？\NAnd the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.66,0:57:43.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不知道\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.61,0:57:58.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,她在干些什么？\NWhat's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.75,0:58:07.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,米歇尔！\NMichelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.61,0:58:31.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊。\NAhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.54,0:58:32.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.88,0:58:35.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.61,0:58:38.38,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.88,0:59:49.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷给我们播放了马特在窝棚找到的录像带\NRay played us the tape that Matt had found in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.86,0:59:53.76,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,如果那卷录像带真的可信的话\NThere's something unexplainable out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.76,0:59:55.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这儿真发生了无法解释的事情\NIf that tape is to be believed,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.86,1:00:00.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那么我就见证了什么鬼东西\Nthen I just witnessed the killing of an entire team of people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.63,1:00:02.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,杀死一整个小队的残忍镜头\Nby something completely unknown.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.94,1:00:05.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,为什么录像带会放到这儿？\NWhy would they send us out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.50,1:00:07.70,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆对这儿发生的事情可以说是痴迷\NSam is so obsessed with what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.71,1:00:10.41,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们犹豫要不要让他看这卷录像带\Nwe're hesitant to even show him the tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.41,1:00:12.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还有霍伊特...\NAnd Hoyt...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.95,1:00:19.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我认为我们该走了\NI think we should go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.82,1:00:21.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不得不离开\NWe have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.99,1:00:28.63,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,但此时此刻，我想他不会做出合理的决定的\NBut I do not think that he is in a place to make decisions right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.63,1:00:30.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那我们到底该干什么\NWhat the hell are we supposed to do then?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.13,1:00:32.73,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我是说我们今晚就走。我们把霍伊特的车开走\NI say we leave tonight. We have Hoyt's truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.90,1:00:35.83,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,站在我身后\NGet behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.47,1:00:42.04,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,上车去\NGet in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.04,1:00:45.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,给我他妈的进车里面去！快点！进车里去！\NGet in the fuckin' truck! Go! Get in the truck!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.91,1:00:48.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,嘿！\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.08,1:00:49.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那东西呢？\NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.48,1:00:50.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨！\NLisa!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.53,1:01:05.03,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,该死！\NShit!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.83,1:01:09.03,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这东西他娘的的在干嘛？\NWhat the fuck is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.03,1:01:11.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，操蛋！\NAh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.87,1:01:18.44,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哪...它去哪儿了？\NWhere did... where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.44,1:01:21.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他跑开了\NHe just ran off.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.61,1:01:24.51,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨，你还好吗？还好吗？\NAre you OK, Lisa? Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.52,1:01:26.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.85,1:01:30.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨。别！别！\NLisa, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.86,1:01:33.62,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？住手！\NWhat are you doing? Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.63,1:01:35.69,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨，住手！\NLisa, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.06,1:01:42.60,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我什么都记不到了。\NI don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.60,1:01:45.04,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,真的\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.04,1:01:47.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们应该要和马特一起走的\NWe should've left with Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.74,1:01:49.91,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,伙计们，我们正在拍摄绝无仅有的录像呢\NWe're getting unprecedented footage, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.91,1:01:51.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这就是我们想要的啊。我们不就是为了这个才来的吗\NThis is what we wanted. This is why we came here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.64,1:01:52.68,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,这是我们想要的？有人都受伤了。\NThis is what we wanted? People are getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.68,1:01:54.14,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，你在胡说些什么？\NWhat are you talking about, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.15,1:01:57.71,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，这是只有我们才掌握的信息\NLook, I think the thing is a single intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.72,1:02:00.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，为了...  你知道些什么？\NOh, for... you know something?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.19,1:02:02.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你疯了\NYou're out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.15,1:02:05.59,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听着，我们如此接近。就差一点\NLook, we are so close. We are right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.59,1:02:07.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,接近什么？\NClose to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.66,1:02:11.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,要是这东西可以变成宝珠会怎么样？或者狼呢？或者甚至科迪呢？\NWhat if this thing can turn into an orb or a wolf or even Cody?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.13,1:02:12.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,或者变成我吗？\NOr me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.66,1:02:15.20,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，说真的，谈话已经他妈的结束了。\NSam, seriously, it's fuckin' done.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.20,1:02:16.97,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，我不想在这儿呆下去了\NI don't want to be here anymore, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.97,1:02:19.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不能在这儿呆下去了。\NI can't be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.00,1:02:20.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,收拾好你的行李。5分钟内在前门碰面\NGo pack your bag. I'll meet you at the front door in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.77,1:02:22.54,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好的，我们离开吧\NOk, we are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.54,1:02:24.57,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你不会去哪儿的吧。卡梅隆，求你了。\NYou're not going anywhere. Cameron, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.58,1:02:28.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,把你的猪蹄子挪开。萨姆，结束了！\NGet your hands off me. It's done, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.08,1:02:31.58,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 好吧，我可不走。 - 都结束了！别说了！\N- Well, I'm not leaving! - It's over! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.56,1:02:42.30,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,8月17号
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.84,1:03:26.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪\NCody.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.04,1:03:28.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,科迪！\NCody!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.92,1:03:42.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,布莱顿，我拿了你的包\NI got your bag, Britain.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.89,1:03:44.35,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,准备好了\NI'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.19,1:03:48.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,都好了吗\NWe ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.66,1:03:50.13,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆呢？\NWhat about Sam?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.13,1:03:51.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他不听劝告。我们叫人再过来\NHe won't listen. We'll send somebody back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.16,1:03:53.10,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,谁给萨姆灌了药喝？\NWho gives a shit about Sam?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.80,1:03:56.00,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷？\NRay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.74,1:04:02.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卡梅隆，他妈的是什么？\NWhat the fuck is this, Cameron?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.37,1:04:07.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊。哦，天啊\NOh, my God. Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.62,1:04:15.75,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快点！快点！丽萨，我们走吧\NCome on. Come on. Let's go, Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.75,1:04:17.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,走！\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.04,1:04:33.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,早上他们会第一时间派辆货车过来\NThey're sending a van first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.77,1:04:35.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,早上？\NIn the morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.21,1:04:37.27,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,丽萨，那是到这儿最快的速度了\NThat's the soonest they can get here, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.28,1:04:38.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，那... 太好了\NThat... that's great, Sam,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.98,1:04:40.78,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,想我们出去正准备离开这儿的时候\Nconsidering we were just out in Hoyt's driveway
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.78,1:04:42.25,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,看到他的车已经面目不堪\Nand his truck was completely disassembled
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.25,1:04:43.68,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们还没遇到过这样见鬼的事呢\Nand we didn't hear a God damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.68,1:04:45.65,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,- 你们随时离开都行 - 怎样离开？\N- Leave anytime you want. - How?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.65,1:04:48.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你没发现那很怪吗？\NDo you find it odd that the moment we arrived on this ranch
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.85,1:04:50.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们一来到这儿这些该死的怪事就接连不断\Nis when all this shit started happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.82,1:04:52.36,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,他是对的。我们可能是MDE实验的一部分呢\NHe's right. We could be part of a MDE experiment...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.36,1:04:54.16,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么？你在胡扯吧\Nwhat are you talking about? You should know better.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.16,1:04:56.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那怎么解释这儿所发生的一切呢？\NHow do you explain what's been happening here?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.66,1:04:59.96,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，那你怎么就知道MDE不了解这儿确切的情况呢？\NHow do you know MDE doesn't know exactly what's here, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.97,1:05:01.93,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不应该让你们来这儿的\NI never should've asked you to come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.44,1:05:06.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,没事了。我们就要回家了\NOk.We're going to get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.37,1:05:09.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,看着我。我们就要回家了\NLook at me.We're going to get home.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.98,1:05:56.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卡梅隆，雷好像有点不对劲\NCameron, there's something wrong with Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.00,1:06:10.43,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,雷？\NRay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.11,1:06:19.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,喔。雷，把枪放下\NWhoa. Put the gun down, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.48,1:06:22.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,好吗？就... 好的\NAll right? Just... Ok.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.01,1:06:23.88,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我不想...\NI don't want...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.88,1:06:26.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.18,1:06:28.99,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.10,1:06:45.77,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.82,1:07:03.12,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,走\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.26,1:07:06.82,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就现在快点！\NCome on now!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.00,1:07:20.94,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，天啊\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.44,1:07:24.21,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，操蛋\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.55,1:07:33.85,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,听我说。你走。你去车子那儿\NListen to me. You go. You get the ATV.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.85,1:07:36.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,走啊！走啊！\NGo! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.33,1:07:44.46,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,开门啊！\NOpen the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.46,1:07:46.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快开啊！\NOpen it!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.33,1:07:48.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,退后点！\NGet back!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.01,1:07:57.57,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,她不见了。她不见了\NShe's gone. She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.49,1:08:11.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在饲料仓里面！快点！\NIn the barn.Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.39,1:08:18.49,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆\NSam!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.87,1:08:23.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,喔\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.64,1:08:29.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快点！快点\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.01,1:08:30.17,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,卡梅隆\NCameron!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.18,1:08:32.18,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆，等一下\NHang on, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.02,1:08:41.42,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,萨姆\NSam!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.10,1:08:53.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.51,1:09:06.48,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,啊\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.46,1:11:09.33,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,未来还在继续\N{\i1}The future's holding on{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.33,1:11:16.50,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，早就该让我撒手\N{\i1}Oh, suspend me in my past{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.50,1:11:19.37,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我就这样醒来\N{\i1}And this is how I woke up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.27,1:11:25.34,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,独自一人\N{\i1}Alone{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.34,1:11:28.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,独自一人\N{\i1}Alone{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.84,1:12:02.45,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,细绳把你荡在\N{\i1}You're dangling by a string{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.45,1:12:07.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,万事之上\N{\i1}Above everything you could be {\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.42,1:12:14.29,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你就这样醒来\N{\i1}And this is how you woke up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.39,1:12:18.06,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,独自一人\N{\i1}Alone{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.66,1:12:22.96,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,借用你的脖子\N{\i1}Sharpen their teeth{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.43,1:12:26.74,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,磨出一口尖牙\N{\i1}On your neck{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.74,1:12:29.07,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还记得你的缺陷\N{\i1}Remember your flaws{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.07,1:12:32.61,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,就像一个坏坏的梦\N{\i1}Like a bad dream{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.11,1:12:36.55,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你执意要醒来\N{\i1}You want to wake up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.55,1:12:45.92,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,快醒来吧\N{\i1}Please wake up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.92,1:12:51.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，快醒来吧\N{\i1}Oh, please wake up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.86,1:12:58.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，快醒来吧\N{\i1}Oh, please wake up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.67,1:13:04.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，快醒来吧\N{\i1}Oh, please wake up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.48,1:13:12.08,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,哦，还有时间\N{\i1}Oh, there's still time{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.39,1:13:27.66,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们凝望一刻也好\N{\i1}Just for a moment as we stare {\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.66,1:13:30.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,在空气中注入我们的思念\N{\i1} Projecting our thoughts into the air {\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.67,1:13:33.84,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,要是以前就这样该多好\N{\i1}As if we had practiced it before{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.84,1:13:36.64,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们手拉手让思想纵容\N{\i1}Our minds danced hand in hand /i>{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.64,1:13:40.01,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们的生活早已注定\N{\i1} And choreographed by both our lives{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.01,1:13:43.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,用眼睛讲述相同的故事\N{\i1}Told like stories to our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.15,1:13:46.15,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,世界迟早都会安静\N{\i1}All of the world frozen in time{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.15,1:13:48.75,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们就这样醒来\N{\i1}And this is how we woke up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.75,1:13:52.72,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,还记得自己是谁\N{\i1}And we remember who we are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.72,1:13:55.86,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,我们穿过黑暗\N{\i1}We were passing in the dark{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.86,1:13:58.89,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,仿佛就沐浴在阳光下面\N{\i1} As if we're something in the light{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.90,1:14:06.67,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,你知道我们都很极端\N{\i1}We're left you know{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.67,1:14:11.47,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,都很极端\N{\i1}Left you know!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.48,1:14:17.98,微软雅黑,,0,0,0,,那一刻你不再失败\N{\i1}When you won't even fail{\i}
